Overview of Changes in Namazu 2.0 - Feb 20, 2000

* NLS support using GNU gettext is added.
* Using GNU automake-1.4.
* Namazu core search engine library is provided.
* Using GNU libtool-1.3.3.
* Access control support by NMZ.access.
* Perl XSUB module support for mknmz is added.
* Using File::MMagic perl module for guess file type.
* Many filters for file processing. (MS Word, PDF, TeX etc.)
* Check point (Re-execute) support for mknmz.
* Replace URL basename in namazurc.
* New nmz-config helper script.
* Documentations are rewritten.
